# AU Micro-SaaS Portfolio — Cursor Pro Models Only
# A$20/mo Cursor Pro | 50-55 bets | cheap workhorse + high-end architect

## Constraint: Cursor Pro models only
All development AI runs through the Cursor IDE model picker.
No external API keys (OpenAI, Anthropic, etc.) for building.
Your A$20/mo usage pool covers everything — stay within it via smart routing.

